            <p>We Believe In Satisfying And Delighting Our Customers. We Are Always Looking Forward To Giving You The Best Of Products At The Best Of Prices And With The Best Of Hopes That We Continue Our Relations Till Time Abides With Your Love For Things Indian! However, If Due To Some Unforeseen Situation You Require The Return Of The Product Then The Following Terms Apply For A Mutually Consented Return.</p>

